WEBVTT

00:16.390 --> 00:19.720
-I have something to tell you.
-I have something to tell you.

00:19.920 --> 00:21.030
I can't go with you.

00:22.230 --> 00:24.030
I've decided to go to Ximeng Pass

00:24.160 --> 00:25.890
to fight against the Yong Army.

00:26.030 --> 00:28.640
I always thought
the people here needed me.

00:28.760 --> 00:31.120
But yesterday,
I finally realized the truth.

00:31.120 --> 00:32.600
It's not that they need me,

00:33.330 --> 00:34.080
but rather,

00:34.790 --> 00:35.750
I need them.

00:37.520 --> 00:40.650
All along, I've wanted to build
a world of true equality—

00:40.790 --> 00:42.350
a place people like me

00:42.840 --> 00:45.710
could finally call home.

00:46.070 --> 00:48.400
I can't go off with you
to live a quiet life.

00:49.000 --> 00:50.520
That's not what I want.

00:52.320 --> 00:53.280
I am Chu Qiao,

00:54.200 --> 00:55.800
commander of the Xiuli Army.

00:56.470 --> 00:59.130
Only when clad in armor,
fighting for my ideals—

00:59.350 --> 01:00.810
for those whose lives were

01:00.920 --> 01:02.560
once worthless, as mine was—

01:02.560 --> 01:03.840
am I truly General Chu.

01:04.510 --> 01:06.120
That is my true self.

01:13.200 --> 01:13.930
Come with me.

01:30.840 --> 01:31.680
Zhuge Yue...

01:33.509 --> 01:35.000
You knew my choice?

01:35.710 --> 01:36.789
This is for you.

01:38.280 --> 01:39.400
I'll go with you.

03:06.120 --> 03:11.410
[REBIRTH]

03:11.840 --> 03:14.460
[Episode 32]

03:20.680 --> 03:22.800
I've only been in Ximeng for a few months,

03:22.800 --> 03:25.240
yet turmoil has arisen
both internally and externally.

03:25.240 --> 03:27.300
I know there has been much discussion

03:27.310 --> 03:28.770
and speculation about me.

03:29.079 --> 03:31.000
I don't know where I was born.

03:31.710 --> 03:33.240
From my earliest memories,

03:33.680 --> 03:36.140
I was a slave in Qingshan Manor
of Great Yong,

03:36.240 --> 03:38.150
one among thousands.

03:38.360 --> 03:40.020
Our lives were worth nothing.

03:40.750 --> 03:43.680
Even survival itself was a luxury.

03:43.800 --> 03:45.710
I watched with my own eyes
as fellow slaves

03:45.710 --> 03:47.430
died one after another.

03:48.400 --> 03:49.280
Before I even

03:49.280 --> 03:51.340
had time to look at them one last time,

03:51.560 --> 03:53.280
their bodies were thrown onto
heaps of bodies

03:53.280 --> 03:54.430
or into mass graves.

03:54.750 --> 03:56.950
The day I escaped from Zhenhuangcheng,

03:57.000 --> 03:58.280
I made up my mind:

03:58.520 --> 03:59.520
in this world,

04:00.360 --> 04:01.750
there should be a place

04:03.030 --> 04:04.430
where no matter who you are,

04:04.430 --> 04:05.680
no matter your birth,

04:05.960 --> 04:07.590
you are not treated as ants

04:07.910 --> 04:08.870
or dust.

04:09.150 --> 04:10.680
There should be justice.

04:10.750 --> 04:11.800
Only such a place

04:12.590 --> 04:14.390
can truly be called my homeland.

04:14.470 --> 04:15.750
That is my faith!

04:16.040 --> 04:17.310
And that is why

04:17.310 --> 04:18.560
I came here.

04:18.560 --> 04:20.959
I wanted to change this place
with your King

04:21.240 --> 04:22.360
and protect it.

04:30.160 --> 04:31.190
Now,

04:31.190 --> 04:34.159
Great Yong's army has been stationed
at Ximeng Pass for days.

04:34.159 --> 04:35.560
Everything they've done

04:35.680 --> 04:36.720
is because they can't tolerate

04:36.720 --> 04:38.390
Ximeng's independence and rise!

04:38.390 --> 04:39.190
Soldiers,

04:39.360 --> 04:40.950
if you're willing to trust me,

04:40.950 --> 04:43.800
march out with me tomorrow to Ximeng Pass,

04:43.920 --> 04:45.560
fight against the Great Yong Army,

04:45.560 --> 04:46.920
defend this land,

04:46.920 --> 04:48.560
and guard our freedom!

04:50.750 --> 04:51.480
General Chu,

04:52.040 --> 04:53.600
the Xiuli Army will always follow you!

04:53.600 --> 04:54.190
Your Majesty,

04:54.190 --> 04:55.950
I, Meng En, will always follow you!

04:55.950 --> 04:57.300
Always follow you!

04:57.390 --> 04:58.830
Always follow you!

04:58.830 --> 05:00.070
Always follow you!

05:00.310 --> 05:01.680
Always follow you!

05:12.000 --> 05:12.800
Young Master,

05:13.000 --> 05:15.240
we really can't leave now, right?

05:15.630 --> 05:16.600
We can't leave.

05:17.510 --> 05:18.570
If the Queen stays,

05:19.560 --> 05:21.160
the King won't leave either.

05:35.540 --> 05:36.250
Yue Shiyi!

05:36.920 --> 05:38.520
What are you thinking about?

05:43.360 --> 05:44.190
I was just wondering

05:44.190 --> 05:46.990
why Lady Chu wouldn't leave
with the Young Master.

05:47.040 --> 05:49.000
Why would she rather live this dangerous,

05:49.000 --> 05:50.310
precarious life?

05:50.480 --> 05:51.070
Tell me,

05:51.750 --> 05:54.190
who would turn down
a life of leisure and comfort

05:54.190 --> 05:54.720
and insist on...

05:54.720 --> 05:55.920
Stop trying to figure it out.

05:55.920 --> 05:57.390
You never would anyway.

06:01.720 --> 06:02.850
It's a victory cake.

06:03.600 --> 06:05.070
How do you know how to make this?

06:05.070 --> 06:06.160
Of course I do.

06:06.190 --> 06:08.700
I grew up in Zhenhuangcheng too.

06:11.390 --> 06:11.950
Minglu,

06:12.600 --> 06:13.510
this tastes

06:13.800 --> 06:15.270
exactly like that shop I used to eat at

06:15.270 --> 06:16.530
in the Shiba District.

06:17.270 --> 06:18.600
Have you eaten there...

06:20.320 --> 06:20.880
Minglu!

06:21.060 --> 06:22.060
Don't follow me!

06:22.630 --> 06:23.680
You can only have that piece.

06:23.680 --> 06:24.600
The rest

06:24.600 --> 06:27.000
is for the soldiers marching out tomorrow.

06:32.750 --> 06:34.600
Our forces will split into six units

06:34.600 --> 06:37.360
and enter the Black River Valley
from these three directions.

06:37.360 --> 06:39.070
I've already had scouts map it out.

06:39.070 --> 06:41.310
There are several low-lying areas here
suitable for ambush.

06:41.310 --> 06:43.360
By then, we'll catch them off guard.

06:44.070 --> 06:44.830
Your Majesty,

06:44.830 --> 06:46.190
our men have just sent word

06:46.190 --> 06:47.240
that a large number of

06:47.240 --> 06:48.630
Ximeng troops are gathering at
the Black River mine.

06:48.630 --> 06:49.830
Where did those troops come from?

06:49.830 --> 06:51.430
We haven't seen them before either.

06:51.430 --> 06:52.680
But from the way they are moving,

06:52.680 --> 06:54.000
they seem to be withdrawing from the mine

06:54.000 --> 06:55.930
and heading towards Ximengcheng.

06:57.159 --> 06:57.960
You may leave.

06:58.270 --> 06:59.330
Yes, Your Majesty.

07:02.630 --> 07:05.030
Zhuge Yue has already
seen through my ploy.

07:06.720 --> 07:09.070
Suddenly withdrawing the troops like this

07:09.070 --> 07:10.190
is really strange.

07:13.160 --> 07:14.820
Your Majesty, General Cheng,

07:15.360 --> 07:16.720
our spies in Ximengcheng

07:16.720 --> 07:17.800
have just sent word

07:17.920 --> 07:21.190
that Great Yong has stationed troops
along the Ximeng borders for days.

07:21.190 --> 07:23.000
King Ximeng has recalled

07:23.000 --> 07:24.240
the border garrison

07:24.510 --> 07:26.760
and is marching south with Queen Ximeng
toward Ximeng Pass

07:26.760 --> 07:28.090
to resist the Yong Army.

07:28.430 --> 07:30.760
Great Yong has sent troops to Ximeng Pass?

07:31.190 --> 07:32.800
Is this intelligence accurate?

07:32.800 --> 07:34.120
Absolutely.

07:34.310 --> 07:35.920
Queen Ximeng has already led the forces

07:35.920 --> 07:37.360
towards Ximeng Pass.

07:37.720 --> 07:39.000
The one Great Yong has sent to
oversee the campaign

07:39.000 --> 07:40.000
is Zhuge Muqing.

07:40.270 --> 07:42.000
He's brought an imperial decree
from the Emperor of Great Yong

07:42.000 --> 07:44.360
to grant amnesty
to King Ximeng and Queen Ximeng.

07:44.360 --> 07:45.159
Your Majesty,

07:45.510 --> 07:47.510
it seems we're not the only ones
after Ximeng's black gold mines.

07:47.510 --> 07:49.600
It seems Great Yong can no longer
stand by either.

07:49.600 --> 07:51.510
Why don't we strike amidst this chaos?

07:51.510 --> 07:53.240
The timing could not be better.

07:53.870 --> 07:54.920
Pass the order—

07:56.070 --> 07:57.190
we set out at once!

07:57.870 --> 07:58.930
Yes, Your Majesty!

08:10.720 --> 08:11.780
Pass down my order—

08:11.870 --> 08:12.930
change direction.

08:13.160 --> 08:14.270
We're heading to Ximeng Pass!

08:14.270 --> 08:15.000
Your Majesty,

08:15.000 --> 08:16.750
the Yong Army numbers in
the tens of thousands outside Ximengcheng,

08:16.750 --> 08:18.270
while we have fewer than
2,000 Black Eagle Army soldiers.

08:18.270 --> 08:20.160
If we lead them all to reinforce Ximeng,

08:20.160 --> 08:22.560
it would be no more than
a drop in the bucket.

08:27.160 --> 08:28.950
Since the battle at Longyin Pass,

08:28.950 --> 08:30.310
we've already reduced conscription

08:30.310 --> 08:32.360
by two levies per year
in order to win over the tribal chiefs.

08:32.360 --> 08:33.630
Now, apart from General Shiyan's

08:33.630 --> 08:34.960
Great Yan Army forces,

08:35.440 --> 08:38.570
we have fewer than
2,000 Black Eagle Army soldiers left.

08:38.840 --> 08:39.909
If we mobilize now,

08:40.030 --> 08:40.600
it would be no different from...

08:40.600 --> 08:41.059
Helian.

08:42.000 --> 08:42.799
Your Majesty.

08:43.320 --> 08:45.450
Are you willing to do something for me?

08:45.630 --> 08:47.360
Please go ahead, Your Majesty.

08:47.510 --> 08:49.080
You must carefully remember

08:49.080 --> 08:50.200
what I'm about to say.

08:50.200 --> 08:52.030
When Elder Tubu of the Hongchuan Tribe
was still alive,

08:52.030 --> 08:53.760
they had 10,000 elite cavalry.

08:53.870 --> 08:55.870
They were Tubu's private soldiers.

08:56.150 --> 08:57.480
Although Tubu is dead,

08:57.480 --> 08:59.000
those troops should still exist

08:59.000 --> 09:01.320
and be managed by his brother Haqi.

09:02.200 --> 09:04.000
The Pale Tribe excels in forging armor,

09:04.000 --> 09:06.460
and their elder commands 3,000 crossbowmen

09:06.480 --> 09:07.910
and 2,000 armored cavalry.

09:07.910 --> 09:09.080
They're also private soldiers.

09:09.080 --> 09:10.410
And the Baichuan Tribe—

09:10.510 --> 09:12.200
they have 3,000 private soldiers.

09:12.200 --> 09:13.670
The Lanchuan Tribe also has 3,000.

09:13.670 --> 09:14.870
Altogether,

09:15.150 --> 09:16.880
there are more than 20,000 men.

09:18.270 --> 09:21.000
I want you, acting in your capacity
as my consort,

09:21.150 --> 09:22.810
to go and borrow these troops.

09:23.360 --> 09:24.600
Your Majesty means...

09:24.600 --> 09:25.150
"Borrow"

09:26.120 --> 09:28.050
is simply another word for "take."

09:28.390 --> 09:29.550
These tribe chiefs

09:29.550 --> 09:30.910
each have their own agendas.

09:30.910 --> 09:32.110
Since my father died,

09:32.510 --> 09:35.040
they've been
quietly expanding their power,

09:35.080 --> 09:37.630
fearing that
if my family were ever to fall,

09:37.840 --> 09:39.570
they'd be dragged down with us.

09:40.840 --> 09:42.480
For the sake of Great Yan's stability,

09:42.480 --> 09:44.140
I've pretended not to notice.

09:44.510 --> 09:47.270
But in truth, I've long since
investigated their full strength.

09:47.270 --> 09:48.480
So, Your Majesty

09:48.480 --> 09:50.200
wants me, in my capacity as your consort,

09:50.200 --> 09:51.600
to request those troops.

09:51.670 --> 09:52.320
First,

09:53.030 --> 09:55.080
it can maintain the appearance
of stability in the country.

09:55.080 --> 09:55.750
Second,

09:56.120 --> 09:57.480
it can also strike fear into them,

09:57.480 --> 09:58.600
making them aware

09:58.840 --> 10:00.080
that their intentions

10:00.080 --> 10:01.480
have not gone unnoticed,

10:01.870 --> 10:03.960
and forcing them to hand over their troops

10:03.960 --> 10:05.630
for Your Majesty to command.

10:08.720 --> 10:09.380
Cheng Yuan,

10:10.030 --> 10:11.090
bring Jing with you

10:11.200 --> 10:13.790
and escort the Consort back to the capital
at full speed to request troops.

10:13.790 --> 10:14.990
Once you secure them,

10:15.550 --> 10:18.200
remain in Great Yan
to guard the capital for me.

10:20.630 --> 10:21.750
Understood.

10:37.030 --> 10:38.110
Look, Your Highness.

10:38.110 --> 10:39.250
These are black-furred donkeys,

10:39.250 --> 10:40.650
a breed unique to Yanbei.

10:41.030 --> 10:42.960
Over there are Guanzhong donkeys,

10:43.200 --> 10:45.200
Hexi donkeys, and spotted donkeys.

10:45.270 --> 10:46.480
There are also
Jingzhou donkeys over there.

10:46.480 --> 10:47.840
See which one you like.

10:49.510 --> 10:52.000
Why do none of them look quite right?

10:54.120 --> 10:54.920
That can't be.

10:55.510 --> 10:57.720
There are only so many
breeds of donkeys in the world.

10:57.720 --> 10:59.120
Your Highness, just pick

10:59.320 --> 11:01.150
the finest one and send it over.

11:01.270 --> 11:02.480
It'll definitely work.

11:02.480 --> 11:04.080
Zhenhuangcheng is far away.

11:04.200 --> 11:05.800
Having that donkey sent here

11:06.000 --> 11:07.800
would take well over two months.

11:07.960 --> 11:09.840
More to the point, if word gets out

11:10.440 --> 11:12.630
that Your Highness had a donkey sent

11:12.720 --> 11:14.250
all the way to the border...

11:14.750 --> 11:16.950
that would be quite the laughingstock.

11:21.390 --> 11:22.080
Then...

11:22.390 --> 11:23.000
this one.

11:24.100 --> 11:24.670
Yes.

11:53.960 --> 11:54.760
General Huan.

11:55.750 --> 11:57.550
I didn't break my promise, did I?

12:01.910 --> 12:03.170
You dare to deceive me!

12:03.790 --> 12:04.960
I didn't.

12:05.360 --> 12:06.790
That is your donkey.

12:06.790 --> 12:08.870
Look, the donkey is perfectly fine—

12:08.960 --> 12:11.000
sturdy, dark, and plump.

12:11.000 --> 12:12.840
That's not my donkey at all.

12:13.910 --> 12:15.360
That is your donkey.

12:15.480 --> 12:17.240
Why would I, a prince of Great Yong,

12:17.240 --> 12:18.750
lie to you over a donkey?

12:21.550 --> 12:22.680
This donkey of yours

12:22.870 --> 12:24.750
is indeed a Great Yan black-furred donkey.

12:24.750 --> 12:25.910
But mine

12:26.030 --> 12:28.550
is a crossbreed of a Great Yan
black-furred donkey and a Hexi donkey.

12:28.550 --> 12:30.240
So its coat looks black,

12:30.360 --> 12:31.890
but its underbelly is gray.

12:33.200 --> 12:34.550
And its mane...

12:36.200 --> 12:37.000
is also wrong.

12:37.910 --> 12:40.120
Perhaps it couldn't adapt to the climate,

12:40.120 --> 12:42.200
causing its coat and appearance to change.

12:42.200 --> 12:43.550
And turned a male donkey
into a female one?

12:43.550 --> 12:44.320
Male donkey?

12:47.630 --> 12:48.670
Alright, alright.

12:48.670 --> 12:49.670
It's my fault.

12:50.120 --> 12:51.840
You may not know this, General Huan,

12:51.840 --> 12:54.100
but there are several donkeys in my camp.

12:54.750 --> 12:56.790
I might have mixed them up

12:56.960 --> 12:58.600
and brought this female donkey by mistake.

12:58.600 --> 13:01.060
But this is also
a fine black-furred donkey.

13:01.240 --> 13:03.000
If you don't mind, General Huan,

13:03.000 --> 13:04.480
how about taking this female donkey

13:04.480 --> 13:06.080
to replace your male one?

13:06.320 --> 13:07.960
I don't want your stupid donkey.

13:07.960 --> 13:10.320
I want my male donkey.

13:10.670 --> 13:11.550
General Huan,

13:12.120 --> 13:13.390
they are all donkeys.

13:13.480 --> 13:14.810
What's the difference?

13:27.150 --> 13:27.680
Let's go!

13:52.550 --> 13:54.670
They can't have gone far!
Search carefully!

13:54.670 --> 13:55.200
Yes, sir!

13:55.270 --> 13:56.480
You, that way!

13:56.630 --> 13:57.720
Yes! Let's go!

14:00.960 --> 14:02.090
Your leg is injured.

14:04.000 --> 14:05.270
There's a small path ahead.

14:05.270 --> 14:06.470
Let's leave quickly.

14:07.150 --> 14:07.670
Go.

14:27.600 --> 14:28.910
You traitors!

14:35.960 --> 14:37.270
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

14:37.270 --> 14:38.600
You think you can save them?

14:38.600 --> 14:40.790
All the Yong guards along the way
have been replaced.

14:40.790 --> 14:42.390
They're all here to kill you.

14:50.870 --> 14:51.630
Calm down.

14:52.120 --> 14:53.850
I've been through this before.

14:54.080 --> 14:55.080
Take my advice—

14:55.720 --> 14:56.600
if you go now,

14:56.910 --> 14:58.710
you'll only die alongside them.

15:01.510 --> 15:02.390
Kill them all.

15:43.440 --> 15:44.500
You're a grown man,

15:44.670 --> 15:47.870
yet you whimper more than the girls
at Zuiyue Restaurant.

15:49.630 --> 15:51.550
Were you framed because someone saw you

15:51.550 --> 15:52.600
as a threat?

15:53.120 --> 15:54.080
How did you know?

15:58.630 --> 16:00.670
I've been dealt with like that before.

16:00.670 --> 16:02.080
Though my men survived,

16:02.320 --> 16:03.520
I nearly lost my life.

16:03.840 --> 16:05.080
You met me at a time

16:05.910 --> 16:08.170
when I couldn't even return to Great Yan.

16:08.270 --> 16:09.600
Then you must be like me—

16:10.270 --> 16:13.070
unaccustomed to the rules
of the imperial family,

16:13.240 --> 16:14.970
yet forced to live within them.

16:16.720 --> 16:18.870
Since you've described it so precisely,

16:18.870 --> 16:20.960
you should've
made your peace with it by now.

16:20.960 --> 16:22.720
My mother died when I was young.

16:23.320 --> 16:25.200
I spent my years
fighting alongside the army.

16:25.200 --> 16:26.600
I used to naively believe

16:27.240 --> 16:29.370
that as long as I earned military merit

16:30.000 --> 16:31.400
and defended Great Yong,

16:31.870 --> 16:33.530
my father would appreciate me

16:33.960 --> 16:34.750
and love me.

16:40.150 --> 16:41.360
But I never expected

16:43.080 --> 16:44.140
that all my efforts

16:44.790 --> 16:46.550
would earn only his suspicion

16:47.080 --> 16:47.910
and wariness.

16:48.670 --> 16:50.720
He favors my thirteenth brother instead.

16:50.720 --> 16:53.180
Even though he's violent and bloodthirsty,

16:54.150 --> 16:55.790
my father still loves him.

17:02.360 --> 17:03.480
What happened today

17:03.480 --> 17:05.609
was your thirteenth brother's doing?

17:05.640 --> 17:06.400
I don't know.

17:07.270 --> 17:09.130
But I must find out when I get back.

17:09.240 --> 17:10.589
How will you investigate?

17:10.589 --> 17:12.200
I have a group of old subordinates

17:12.200 --> 17:14.130
stationed 50 li away in Yan County.

17:14.200 --> 17:15.720
I'll go meet up with them shortly.

17:15.720 --> 17:16.750
Fifty li away?

17:18.310 --> 17:19.640
With that injured leg?

17:20.680 --> 17:21.480
General Huan,

17:23.069 --> 17:23.720
I...

17:26.960 --> 17:27.920
Eat this.

17:33.590 --> 17:34.650
I'm going to sleep.

17:39.000 --> 17:41.260
We'll depart tomorrow and make it quick.

17:52.830 --> 17:53.790
Nonsense.

17:55.030 --> 17:56.160
They sent this?

17:56.720 --> 17:57.160
Yes.

17:58.350 --> 17:59.200
What is this?

17:59.790 --> 18:00.990
This document claims

18:01.110 --> 18:02.750
I'm the daughter of

18:02.750 --> 18:04.400
the Emperor of Great Yong
and a slave girl.

18:04.400 --> 18:06.400
Back then, that slave was pregnant

18:06.400 --> 18:07.480
and feared being killed,

18:07.480 --> 18:09.200
so she fled Jinsheng Palace overnight

18:09.200 --> 18:10.500
and was saved by the Jing family.

18:10.500 --> 18:11.260
This paper

18:10.520 --> 18:12.530
[Great Yong Slave Registry]

18:11.810 --> 18:13.340
is her slave registration.

18:13.880 --> 18:15.410
These childhood keepsakes

18:15.590 --> 18:18.720
are said to be mine
from when I lived with the Jing family.

18:18.720 --> 18:20.790
These are just ordinary old items.

18:21.110 --> 18:22.400
How do they prove anything?

18:22.400 --> 18:23.660
And this slave record—

18:23.720 --> 18:25.320
you could find one anywhere.

18:25.400 --> 18:26.860
They truly stop at nothing

18:27.240 --> 18:28.750
to seize Ximeng.

18:29.030 --> 18:29.880
Pass my order:

18:30.590 --> 18:33.440
all troops within the pass
are to be on full alert,

18:33.440 --> 18:34.770
rotating day and night,

18:35.000 --> 18:38.000
to prevent the Yong Army
from exploiting any opening.

18:38.750 --> 18:39.350
Yes.

18:54.310 --> 18:55.160
Who are you?

18:55.590 --> 18:57.920
Envoys of Great Yong request an audience.

18:58.110 --> 18:59.030
Your Majesty,

18:59.200 --> 19:00.960
a delegation from Great Yong is
outside the pass, requesting an audience.

19:00.960 --> 19:03.070
They said they want to
present gifts to their princess.

19:03.070 --> 19:04.000
I won't see them!

19:04.400 --> 19:06.440
There is no Great Yong princess in Ximeng.

19:06.440 --> 19:07.500
Pass down my order:

19:08.070 --> 19:10.070
any envoys or troops from Great Yong

19:10.240 --> 19:11.790
are forbidden to enter the pass.

19:11.790 --> 19:12.310
Yes!

19:14.790 --> 19:16.720
Envoys of Great Yong, leave immediately!

19:16.720 --> 19:18.450
You are not permitted to enter!

19:37.790 --> 19:38.590
Your Majesty,

19:38.720 --> 19:40.070
your order has been passed down.

19:40.070 --> 19:41.400
The envoys of Great Yong have left,

19:41.400 --> 19:43.510
but they left some things
outside the pass.

19:43.510 --> 19:44.400
What things?

19:44.750 --> 19:46.590
Just a few carts of grain,
vegetables, and fruits.

19:46.590 --> 19:48.480
They send grain and produce
as gifts to a princess?

19:48.480 --> 19:50.070
Are they humiliating us?

20:06.200 --> 20:06.730
Let's go.

20:09.750 --> 20:10.590
It's grain.

20:12.640 --> 20:13.400
Come. Come on.

20:13.400 --> 20:13.920
Hurry.

20:20.790 --> 20:21.640
Your Majesty,

20:21.640 --> 20:22.960
the people have been taking the food

20:22.960 --> 20:24.510
left by the envoys for the past two days.

20:24.510 --> 20:26.350
Today, they delivered a third batch

20:26.350 --> 20:28.080
and still used the same excuse.

20:29.160 --> 20:29.960
Your Majesty!

20:32.590 --> 20:34.240
The Yong Army has over 10,000 soldiers,

20:34.240 --> 20:35.350
including more than 800 cavalry,

20:35.350 --> 20:36.640
currently encamped 50 li outside the pass.

20:36.640 --> 20:37.790
They've also set up high platforms
to observe the battlefield.

20:37.790 --> 20:38.680
Your Majesty!

20:40.550 --> 20:41.270
Your Majesty,

20:41.270 --> 20:42.920
the Yong Army has brought
a group of our commoners

20:42.920 --> 20:45.580
and is requesting an audience
outside the pass.

20:51.080 --> 20:51.740
Who are you?

20:52.070 --> 20:54.200
How dare you trespass into the palace!

20:56.590 --> 20:57.440
Give this...

20:57.880 --> 20:59.280
Give this to King Ximeng.

20:59.790 --> 21:00.720
Tell him

21:01.280 --> 21:03.130
that the Queen is in danger.

21:12.420 --> 21:15.280
Bandits have been rampant
outside the Ximeng Pass!

21:16.160 --> 21:17.720
Yesterday, we captured a group of bandits

21:17.720 --> 21:19.920
who looted the Princess's gift convoy!

21:20.640 --> 21:22.440
Today, we will publicly execute them

21:22.440 --> 21:23.790
as a warning!

21:32.350 --> 21:33.150
Execute them!

21:35.920 --> 21:37.580
This is the first batch today!

21:38.240 --> 21:40.790
From now on, we'll send
a batch of bandits every day

21:40.790 --> 21:42.440
until the Princess
comes out of the pass herself

21:42.440 --> 21:45.100
to receive Great Yong's
imperial investiture!

22:10.200 --> 22:12.600
Let me share some good news,
Your Highness.

22:13.050 --> 22:14.770
Zhao Che has now been charged

22:14.790 --> 22:16.830
with treason and colluding with the enemy.

22:16.830 --> 22:19.360
This morning,
news arrived from Yanming Pass

22:19.640 --> 22:22.680
that his trusted subordinates in the army
were executed on the spot.

22:22.680 --> 22:24.790
Only he managed to escape by luck.

22:25.160 --> 22:26.640
His fate remains unknown.

22:26.880 --> 22:27.920
Unknown?

22:28.750 --> 22:30.070
Why isn't he dead?

22:30.490 --> 22:32.150
Rest assured, Your Highness.

22:32.590 --> 22:35.270
That means he's as good as dead.

22:35.880 --> 22:37.160
He, a prince,

22:37.510 --> 22:40.710
has colluded with Great Yan
and fled while under charges.

22:41.110 --> 22:42.480
In our father's eyes,

22:42.790 --> 22:45.000
he's no different from a dead man.

22:51.920 --> 22:52.960
Draw carefully.

22:59.160 --> 23:03.000
Princess Chun'er's collarbones
are especially graceful and captivating.

23:03.000 --> 23:04.110
And this necklace

23:04.480 --> 23:05.750
suits her perfectly.

23:08.590 --> 23:11.400
You must capture
her spirit in the painting.

23:12.030 --> 23:13.160
Yes, Your Highness.

23:16.720 --> 23:18.250
Greetings, Your Highness.

23:19.160 --> 23:19.790
What is it?

23:20.790 --> 23:21.850
I've received news

23:22.030 --> 23:24.070
that Chu Qiao has arrived at Ximeng Pass

23:24.070 --> 23:26.200
with only part of the Xiuli Army
and Ximeng soldiers.

23:26.200 --> 23:29.660
Everything is proceeding
according to Your Highness's plan.

23:31.880 --> 23:34.200
Thank you for your assistance, Lord Muhe.

23:34.200 --> 23:35.830
If you hadn't told us

23:35.830 --> 23:37.680
that Zhuge Yue is King Ximeng,

23:37.960 --> 23:39.160
how could Zhuge Muqing

23:39.160 --> 23:40.960
have complied with our orders so easily?

23:40.960 --> 23:42.310
It is my duty.

23:44.160 --> 23:45.350
Rest assured.

23:45.440 --> 23:46.840
When I ascend the throne,

23:47.160 --> 23:48.400
I'll let your family

23:48.590 --> 23:50.830
take over Zhuge Muqing's Qingshan Manor

23:50.830 --> 23:53.720
to avenge your brother, Muhe Xifeng.

23:55.550 --> 23:56.960
Thank you, Your Highness.

23:56.960 --> 23:57.510
Come on!

23:58.030 --> 24:00.090
Let's continue painting the beauty!

24:21.790 --> 24:24.850
Although Ximeng Pass has
natural terrain advantages,

24:25.070 --> 24:27.110
against Great Yong,

24:27.440 --> 24:28.970
we wouldn't stand a chance.

24:29.240 --> 24:31.040
After I leave the pass tomorrow,

24:31.200 --> 24:31.720
He Xiao,

24:32.350 --> 24:33.920
you'll lead all the Ximeng Army

24:33.920 --> 24:35.880
and the Xiuli Army to guard the pass

24:36.480 --> 24:39.480
in case they launch a surprise attack
while we're away.

24:39.480 --> 24:39.960
Yes.

24:41.310 --> 24:41.920
Minglu,

24:43.000 --> 24:45.000
tomorrow you'll accompany me
into the Great Yong camp

24:45.000 --> 24:46.660
to escort the civilians back.

24:47.550 --> 24:48.030
Okay.

24:49.880 --> 24:50.610
Wang Shi'er,

24:51.400 --> 24:53.480
you'll set up an ambush at Crescent Slope.

24:53.480 --> 24:55.830
The terrain here is elevated
with a clear view.

24:55.830 --> 24:57.350
Charging downhill from there

24:57.350 --> 24:58.440
leads straight to the weakest part

24:58.440 --> 24:59.750
of the Great Yong camp.

25:01.000 --> 25:03.060
It'd be best if we could return safely

25:03.240 --> 25:04.240
tomorrow.

25:05.030 --> 25:06.480
But if anything goes wrong,

25:06.480 --> 25:08.440
use the whistling arrow as the signal.

25:08.440 --> 25:10.270
The moment they open the gates
to let the people go, seize it—

25:10.270 --> 25:11.730
charge in and rescue them.

25:13.590 --> 25:14.320
Don't worry.

25:15.070 --> 25:16.870
Crescent Slope is well-hidden.

25:17.200 --> 25:19.510
Most people don't even know
there's a shortcut there.

25:19.510 --> 25:21.110
The Yong Army won't guard it.

25:21.640 --> 25:22.200
My Lady,

25:23.640 --> 25:24.960
this is clearly a deadly trap

25:24.960 --> 25:26.480
the Yong Army has set for you

25:26.480 --> 25:28.510
No matter how thorough our plan is,

25:28.510 --> 25:30.400
we won't be able to respond in time
if something goes wrong.

25:30.400 --> 25:31.260
No matter what,

25:31.960 --> 25:33.090
please be cautious.

25:33.270 --> 25:34.000
Don't worry.

25:35.310 --> 25:37.110
What Great Yong wants is Ximeng.

25:37.270 --> 25:38.680
My life is not what's at stake here.

25:38.680 --> 25:39.830
Since they went to such lengths

25:39.830 --> 25:41.240
to make me a princess,

25:41.960 --> 25:43.420
they won't kill me easily.

26:10.070 --> 26:10.550
Master,

26:11.200 --> 26:13.000
Chu Qiao has really come.

26:20.350 --> 26:20.880
Minglu,

26:21.680 --> 26:22.610
wait for me here.

26:23.310 --> 26:23.680
Yes.

26:31.160 --> 26:32.000
Help!

26:32.270 --> 26:33.830
Please save us!

26:34.400 --> 26:36.680
Your Majesty, save us!

26:36.880 --> 26:38.550
Save us!

26:39.750 --> 26:41.070
Please save us!

26:41.070 --> 26:42.720
Save us!

26:42.720 --> 26:44.680
Please save us!

26:51.440 --> 26:52.200
Miss Chu,

26:53.000 --> 26:55.330
My Lord is already waiting for you inside.

26:56.030 --> 26:57.030
Please follow me.

27:18.070 --> 27:21.270
I never expected the Great Yong envoy

27:21.880 --> 27:24.080
to be you, the Master of Qingshan Manor,

27:24.440 --> 27:26.070
Lord Zhuge Muqing.

27:26.590 --> 27:28.200
General Chu,

27:29.400 --> 27:31.460
please receive the imperial decree.

27:32.070 --> 27:33.480
By the mandate of heaven,

27:34.070 --> 27:35.440
the Emperor decrees:

27:35.720 --> 27:38.960
my daughter Chu Qiao, lost since childhood

27:39.400 --> 27:41.240
and having endured great hardships,

27:41.240 --> 27:43.880
has at last been found.

27:44.030 --> 27:45.510
In recognition of this,

27:45.830 --> 27:49.430
I hereby confer upon her the title
Princess Ximeng of Great Yong,

27:50.000 --> 27:52.070
as a mark of imperial favor

27:52.510 --> 27:55.750
and grace.

28:00.270 --> 28:03.400
Princess Chu Qiao,
please accept the decree.

28:17.440 --> 28:19.270
Can you release them now?

28:28.000 --> 28:28.800
Release them!

28:34.200 --> 28:35.880
Run! Run!

28:40.720 --> 28:42.350
Hurry up! Hurry!

28:42.550 --> 28:43.350
Go, go!

28:44.830 --> 28:45.350
Hurry!

28:45.960 --> 28:46.400
Go!

28:46.960 --> 28:47.590
Hurry up and go!

28:47.590 --> 28:48.070
Hurry!

28:48.070 --> 28:49.240
Hurry up!

28:49.510 --> 28:50.000
Hurry!

28:50.000 --> 28:50.640
Hurry!

28:51.030 --> 28:51.510
Hurry!

28:56.590 --> 28:57.550
Lord Zhuge,

28:58.790 --> 29:00.190
the performance is over.

29:00.350 --> 29:02.210
It's time for the curtain to fall.

29:04.000 --> 29:04.830
Ximeng

29:05.350 --> 29:06.640
will forever remain a land

29:06.640 --> 29:08.370
of self-governance and peace!

29:08.720 --> 29:10.720
We'll never submit to your country!

29:11.270 --> 29:13.070
I am not a princess of Great Yong,

29:13.270 --> 29:15.160
nor will I accept its decree!

29:43.600 --> 29:45.400
Hurry up! Run!

30:04.750 --> 30:05.350
Save them!

30:16.510 --> 30:17.310
An ambush!

31:41.550 --> 31:42.160
My Lady!

31:44.270 --> 31:44.750
My Lady.

31:46.880 --> 31:47.750
Today,

31:48.390 --> 31:50.130
let us fight our way out together!

31:50.130 --> 31:53.260
Then let us kill our way through
with everything we have!

32:14.390 --> 32:15.350
Zhuge Yue...

32:18.710 --> 32:19.350
Xing!

32:29.000 --> 32:29.640
I know

32:30.720 --> 32:32.070
it was your men who sent the Moon Guard

32:32.070 --> 32:34.270
to inform me that Chu Qiao was in danger.

32:34.400 --> 32:35.030
Today,

32:36.000 --> 32:39.660
this was also your scheme to
deliberately lure me here, wasn't it?

32:40.510 --> 32:41.200
Good.

32:41.750 --> 32:44.030
Truly worthy of being my grandson.

32:44.720 --> 32:45.400
Smart.

32:45.480 --> 32:46.400
Let Chu Qiao go,

32:47.350 --> 32:49.550
and I'll go back to
Qingshan Manor with you.

32:49.550 --> 32:51.880
You're in my military camp,

32:52.550 --> 32:55.590
surrounded by
tens of thousands of Great Yong troops.

32:56.000 --> 32:57.240
I can take you and Chu Qiao

32:57.240 --> 33:00.110
back to Great Yong at any moment.

33:01.200 --> 33:01.830
What

33:02.720 --> 33:04.920
makes you think you can bargain with me?

33:08.070 --> 33:11.160
Lord Zhuge, you've presided over
Qingshan Manor for decades

33:11.160 --> 33:13.760
and have fought
alongside the army many times.

33:13.790 --> 33:16.350
Just like me, a former Great Yong
military counselor,

33:16.350 --> 33:17.240
you should be well aware of

33:17.240 --> 33:20.100
the defensive deployments
of Great Yong's passes.

33:21.200 --> 33:22.530
What are you getting at?

33:23.720 --> 33:26.400
Ping'an Pass, Linyuan Pass,
and Qinglong Pass—

33:26.750 --> 33:28.240
these three passes have always been

33:28.240 --> 33:30.970
the weakest points
in Great Yong's defense line.

33:31.310 --> 33:35.440
You're threatening me with Great Yong's

33:35.680 --> 33:36.740
military secrets?

33:39.960 --> 33:40.830
Ping'an Pass—

33:41.200 --> 33:42.830
only 3,000 elite troops
are stationed there.

33:42.830 --> 33:44.440
The defenses are weak,
and the terrain is open—

33:44.440 --> 33:45.880
perfect for a rapid assault.

33:45.880 --> 33:47.110
With just 500 soldiers,

33:47.110 --> 33:48.550
I can breach its defenses

33:48.550 --> 33:49.750
and seize it swiftly.

33:50.310 --> 33:51.200
Linyuan Pass

33:51.750 --> 33:53.280
is guarded by 5,000 troops.

33:53.350 --> 33:55.920
However, the city fortifications
are aging, and morale is low.

33:55.920 --> 33:57.550
If we launch a surprise attack
under cover of night

33:57.550 --> 33:59.200
and exploit the concealment
of the mountain range,

33:59.200 --> 34:00.530
we can take it with ease.

34:00.790 --> 34:01.680
Qinglong Pass

34:01.880 --> 34:03.000
has 4,000 troops.

34:03.000 --> 34:04.310
However, it's located in a remote area

34:04.310 --> 34:05.840
with fragile supply lines.

34:06.030 --> 34:08.630
If I send men to
cut off their provisions first,

34:08.670 --> 34:11.670
the garrison there will be
thrown into desperate straits.

34:11.670 --> 34:13.190
I've already deployed my troops.

34:13.190 --> 34:14.650
If you refuse to let her go,

34:15.510 --> 34:16.639
by tomorrow morning

34:16.760 --> 34:18.190
Ping'an Pass will fall,

34:18.190 --> 34:19.880
Linyuan Pass will be besieged,

34:19.880 --> 34:21.610
and Qinglong Pass will be lost.

34:22.670 --> 34:24.190
I don't need a massive army.

34:24.190 --> 34:25.650
With just 3,000 soldiers,

34:26.110 --> 34:29.710
I can bring consequences upon you
that you cannot afford to bear.

34:36.480 --> 34:37.880
You are

34:38.550 --> 34:39.710
here now.

34:40.590 --> 34:43.150
I can have you seized at any moment.

34:43.590 --> 34:45.840
Even if you've set up
your troops in advance

34:45.840 --> 34:47.880
to attack those passes,

34:48.880 --> 34:50.480
no matter how fast they move,

34:51.230 --> 34:53.030
they won't be faster than my men.

34:54.480 --> 34:55.080
Very well.

34:56.190 --> 34:57.030
Then try it.

34:58.030 --> 34:59.510
I have troops in ambush

34:59.920 --> 35:01.230
all around.

35:02.070 --> 35:04.920
They may not match
tens of thousands of your troops,

35:04.920 --> 35:05.840
but every one of my men

35:05.840 --> 35:08.280
is utterly loyal and fearless.

35:09.550 --> 35:12.080
As for the troops you brought,
General Zhuge,

35:12.400 --> 35:14.600
they were all on loan from General Meng.

35:14.840 --> 35:15.880
Once a conflict breaks out,

35:15.880 --> 35:17.320
the Ximeng soldiers behind me

35:17.320 --> 35:19.230
will be defending their own homeland,

35:19.230 --> 35:22.630
fighting for the very survival
of everything they hold dear.

35:22.960 --> 35:24.920
They will give everything they have.

35:24.920 --> 35:26.800
With everything on the line
and no way to retreat,

35:26.800 --> 35:29.130
your ten thousand troops, General Zhuge,

35:29.760 --> 35:31.090
may be no match for them.

35:40.000 --> 35:40.800
Yue,

35:41.030 --> 35:41.840
I

35:42.710 --> 35:44.400
raised you with my own hands.

35:44.880 --> 35:45.880
I know you.

35:48.150 --> 35:49.360
You wouldn't do this.

35:49.880 --> 35:51.510
You don't have the heart for it.

35:51.510 --> 35:52.760
You wouldn't let the citizens and soldiers

35:52.760 --> 35:55.490
of Great Yong die
by the blades of Ximeng soldiers

35:56.030 --> 35:58.920
for the sake of one woman.

35:59.320 --> 36:00.760
Since you're so certain,

36:01.320 --> 36:02.650
why don't we make a wager

36:02.880 --> 36:04.140
and see if I'll do that?

36:04.630 --> 36:05.110
But...

36:06.030 --> 36:07.400
can you afford to lose?

36:13.880 --> 36:14.480
Master,

36:14.630 --> 36:16.320
Yan Xun has led the Black Eagle Army

36:16.320 --> 36:18.960
to flank us through the secret passage
outside Yanming Mountain.

36:18.960 --> 36:22.020
They've already reached
the outskirts of Ximeng Pass.

36:25.190 --> 36:25.800
Master!

36:30.550 --> 36:32.610
So you'd anticipated this all along.

36:33.230 --> 36:35.480
That's why you dared to come alone...

36:37.670 --> 36:39.230
come alone to negotiate.

36:41.440 --> 36:43.070
I learned this

36:43.630 --> 36:45.030
from you, Grandfather.

36:46.150 --> 36:48.190
When you sent troops
to Ximeng, Grandfather,

36:48.190 --> 36:50.590
did you not also
keep many cards in reserve?

36:55.710 --> 36:56.630
Let Chu Qiao go.

36:57.510 --> 36:59.110
Spare Ximeng and its people.

36:59.800 --> 37:00.730
I'll go with you.

37:03.360 --> 37:04.280
Release them.

37:04.800 --> 37:05.530
Yes, Master.

37:11.030 --> 37:12.430
Thank you, Grandfather.

37:14.440 --> 37:15.710
You can't go!

37:16.840 --> 37:18.710
I'll escort her
to the gates of Ximeng Pass

37:18.710 --> 37:19.640
and then return.

37:20.070 --> 37:21.920
You think I would believe you?

37:23.510 --> 37:24.190
We've...

37:25.230 --> 37:26.360
struck a deal,

37:26.360 --> 37:28.030
and I've released those people.

37:28.030 --> 37:28.800
But

37:29.880 --> 37:33.030
I will absolutely not allow you
to leave this place!

37:34.630 --> 37:35.490
General Zhuge,

37:35.880 --> 37:38.070
what I promised you, I will fulfill.

37:38.360 --> 37:41.090
What I didn't promise,
you cannot compel me to do.

37:41.480 --> 37:43.140
Whether you believe me or not,

37:43.320 --> 37:44.780
you had no choice earlier—

37:45.030 --> 37:45.760
and

37:46.800 --> 37:48.130
you still have none now.

37:50.230 --> 37:51.830
If you insist on stopping me,

37:52.150 --> 37:54.010
then let us see whether your spies

37:54.710 --> 37:56.280
can hold me back.

37:58.480 --> 37:59.710
Zhuge Yue!

37:59.920 --> 38:00.670
No!

38:00.920 --> 38:03.110
Yue, you can't go!

38:03.110 --> 38:05.360
You can't go!

38:07.440 --> 38:09.800
Yue!

38:10.480 --> 38:12.840
Yue!

38:16.840 --> 38:17.590
Master!

38:27.190 --> 38:28.070
Master!

38:54.280 --> 38:54.960
Minglu,

38:55.190 --> 38:56.030
hold in there.

38:56.960 --> 38:58.090
We're almost there.

39:00.070 --> 39:00.920
I'm fine.

39:05.190 --> 39:05.840
Minglu!

39:22.320 --> 39:22.880
Chu!

39:24.040 --> 39:24.710
Chu!

39:24.600 --> 39:26.810
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

39:25.230 --> 39:25.760
Minglu!

39:25.760 --> 39:27.030
Chu, are you alright?

39:26.920 --> 39:29.470
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

39:27.150 --> 39:27.840
I'm fine.

39:28.110 --> 39:28.960
Miss Minglu!

39:29.000 --> 39:29.530
Let's go.

39:29.620 --> 39:30.920
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

39:30.950 --> 39:32.410
♪ My longing surges ♪

39:32.430 --> 39:34.940
♪ I become haggard ♪

39:35.550 --> 39:37.990
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

39:38.030 --> 39:40.850
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

39:39.070 --> 39:39.710
Go!

39:40.880 --> 39:42.580
♪ My love remains ♪

39:42.590 --> 39:43.190
My Lady...

39:42.890 --> 39:46.260
♪ But you're already gone ♪

39:46.280 --> 39:48.560
♪ What I seek in life ♪

39:48.580 --> 39:50.100
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

39:50.120 --> 39:52.770
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

39:52.800 --> 39:57.660
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

39:56.150 --> 39:56.800
Chu.

39:57.680 --> 39:59.080
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

39:57.760 --> 39:58.690
Are you alright?

39:59.100 --> 40:01.350
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

39:59.960 --> 40:01.160
Great Yong's camp...

40:01.380 --> 40:03.820
♪ How do we start over? ♪

40:01.920 --> 40:03.030
Save Zhuge Yue...

40:03.850 --> 40:07.160
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

40:05.360 --> 40:07.960
General Zhuge Muqing has passed away!

40:07.180 --> 40:09.440
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

40:09.460 --> 40:12.870
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

40:12.900 --> 40:15.210
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

40:13.070 --> 40:14.270
Great Yong's camp...

40:15.070 --> 40:16.230
Save Zhuge Yue...

40:15.240 --> 40:18.120
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

40:17.150 --> 40:17.760
Chu!

40:18.140 --> 40:22.680
♪ In the end ♪

40:18.480 --> 40:19.110
Chu!

40:24.240 --> 40:29.620
♪ It can only be praised ♪

40:49.230 --> 40:50.160
In this world...

40:51.280 --> 40:52.030
not everyone

40:52.030 --> 40:53.760
is free to follow their heart.

40:55.070 --> 40:56.070
I'm going to find her.

40:56.070 --> 40:56.630
Chu.

40:56.630 --> 40:57.830
I'm going to find her!

40:57.960 --> 40:58.840
Search the place thoroughly

40:58.840 --> 41:00.360
and seize everyone inside!

41:00.360 --> 41:00.840
Hurry!

41:02.320 --> 41:03.840
He and I grew up together,

41:04.320 --> 41:05.520
as close as brothers.

41:05.710 --> 41:07.310
I know him better than you do.

41:07.840 --> 41:13.480
Welcome back, Young Master!
